## Acknowledgments

This project was created for the Hashgraph Hackathon 2025 and uses:

- Hedera Hashgraph SDK for blockchain interactions
- IPFS for decentralized storage
- Node.js and Express for the backend API
- Various open-source libraries and tools

Special thanks to:
- The Hedera team for providing an excellent blockchain platform
- The IPFS community for decentralized storage solutions
- The Node.js and JavaScript ecosystem contributors
- The Hashgraph Hackathon organizers for the opportunity

